Position- SENIOR AEM/REACT DEVELOPER POSITION

Visa- USC/GC

location - Remote

I would say at least 5 years experience.

Job title:

Sr. AEM/React Developer

Please send anyone you have that has strong React, AEM (Adobe Experience Manager), Java skills

• Designs, codes, tests, and implements programs; develops system documentation according to SAFe Agile principles and industry standards

• Performs unit tests, troubleshoots, and takes required corrective actions as needed for configuration and integration needs.

• Deliver against the optimization and customized experience strategies across our digital offerings on the current shop (checkout product search at the self-checkout lanes, e-commerce and basket building online) to meet SLA/functional requirements.

• Debug code

• MUST be strong in ReactJS (70%) of work, with combination of AEM experience, Java is a plus (15% each) Full Stack Dev may be good

• With AEM must be able to pull product data, not pull web pages.

Qualifications: I would say at least 5 years experience
With AEM must be able to pull product data, not pull web pages
